          <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2018-10-11T19:52:23Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>7(a) Real Estate Appraisal Harmonization Act </b></p> <p>This bill amends the Small Business Act to revise the loan amount above which a real estate appraisal is required for a commercial real property securing a small business loan. Specifically, the bill ties the amount to the federal banking regulator appraisal threshold. (Currently, an appraisal is required for a loan of more than $250,000.)</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-10-05T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
        </item>
